17 (c) It is not a wrongful withholding of security deposit funds if the landlord mails the funds to the
18 last-known address of a tenant who has departed and the tenant does not receive the funds because the tenant
19 has not given the landlord the tenant's new address, but the landlord remains liable to the tenant for the amount
20 due the tenant.
