24 Section 3. Section 70-25-205, MCA, is amended to read:
25 "70-25-205. Failure of departing tenant to furnish new address. (1) Failure by the departing tenant
26 to provide the landlord with a new address in writing upon termination of the tenancy or upon surrender and
27 acceptance of the leasehold premises, whichever occurs first, does not bar the tenant from recovering the
28 amount owing to the tenant by the landlord.
